accessibility.text: We believe that  commitment,  thoroughness, persistence,  self-sacrifice and  perseverance bring results,  while luck and quick  success are fleeting

We believe that ambition  is a necessary motor for  constant improvement. The will to reach the  highest standard of  performance, not just do  things well but as well  as possible, seeking to  improve day by day.
We believe the value of seeing all this clearly,  maintaining and defending  it even in situations of clear  superiority and success.
We believe in personal  relations that are formal  and friendly, above and beyond rules and  regulations.
We believe that individuals  are always part of a group and, as such, their contribution improves  the whole.
